window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sir Crabby McCrabbington, Lord of the Coast and High Crab of the Realm, thought he had escaped the dungeon...</b></p> <p>Only to enter claw first into a wider conflict. Unknown to the rest of the Arthos, the dungeon monsters have fought an unending undersea war against <i>CORRUPTION</i><b>.</b> A conflict that is steadily progressing.</p> <p>Sir Crabby finds himself stuck between new friends, new enemies, and worse as the gods look from on high. With a jaunty tune, and the heart of a hero, he must find the means to survive and escape from the Army of....</p> <p><i>INCURSION CITY.</i></p> <p><b>Bestseller Ryan Rimmel, author of </b><b><i>Noobtown</i></b><b>, teams with Boe Hagen to bring you this hilarious and unique LitRPG Series about the most unlikely of heroes who gains access to a System, and all the wacky adventures that ensue.</b></p>"; 
